casebody.data:
Daly, Respondent, v. Wise, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 12, 1890.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Reynolds & Harrison, for appellant. Daly, Hoyt & Mason, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 7 N. Y. Supp. 902.
